$ /sys/block/_device_

The tree under `/sys/block/_device_` (for example `/sys/bloc/sda`) contains information about a specific → Linux/devices#block-devices.

The file → Linux/fhs/sys/block/_device_/stat[`stat`] provides several statistics about the state of the block device `_device_`.


sa:

 `→ Linux/fhs/sys/block`

 `→ Linux/fhs/proc/diskstats`
